{"tid":2441601,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–老鼠及兔仔會否流汗？","createTime":"2021-03-10T21:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T23:49:32.000Z","uid":38861,"like":83,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"026a00f629c520d863538d3ce4721dbf0866b5f0","tid":2441601,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:40:51.000Z","msg":"人、狗、鼠、兔均是恆溫動物，意思即是他們需要動用從新陳代謝中所獲取的能量來保持恆常體溫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdgZZgo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdgZZgo.jpg&h=a99c2a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在炎熱的天氣下，人及狗均能依靠流汗及喘氣作散熱的手段。<br />\n但鼠及兔皮下並沒有汗腺的關係，牠們沒有流汗的能力，同時亦沒有喘氣的習性。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）在行為方面，鼠及兔只好依靠躲藏或擺出不同的身體姿勢作散溫或保暖用途。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pBo2cBr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpBo2cBr.jpg&h=6c0120c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n生理方面，鼠及兔能透過豎毛(Piloerection)，亦即是毛管戙來阻隔寒氣入侵，又或是擴張血管(Vasodilation)來加快散熱效能。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）老鼠的尾巴約佔全身皮膚面積5%左右，但約17%的體溫調節功能均是透過尾巴的血管擴張及收縮來控制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pw1Gs9O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw1Gs9O.png&h=1a659b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於兔仔的耳廓(Auricle)，其表面的血管亦跟老鼠尾巴帶有著調節溫度的功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=636ef3db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=276ab2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。"},{"pid":"d3af7655169a2700d11970481f6df30d28a3aeda","tid":2441601,"uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:42:03.000Z","msg":"依篇會唔會唔夠深入，或者已經足夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca38ab46249bed9c8b1b9a3cdb614d6fbb227c63","tid":2441601,"uid":255980,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d3af7655169a2700d11970481f6df30d28a3aeda","tid":2441601,"uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:42:03.000Z","msg":"依篇會唔會唔夠深入，或者已經足夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:44:24.000Z","msg":"想學多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7580b8e232f9390ac7462232b6d68d6c1629df","tid":2441601,"uid":100371,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d3af7655169a2700d11970481f6df30d28a3aeda","tid":2441601,"uid":38861,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:42:03.000Z","msg":"依篇會唔會唔夠深入，或者已經足夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T21:47:39.000Z","msg":"可以再深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d357bcedf7734474b43191bf58d0843825aad7","tid":2441601,"uid":62811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T22:00:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9d10979856b6ef5b81b96bdedb412bb79